Frizerkin muz

3
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:13,397
Za Zazu, koja ce se prepoznati.

4
00:02:54,391 --> 00:02:56,868
Moj um je zbrkan
secanjima...

5
00:02:57,787 --> 00:03:00,105
Sve je pocelo na plazi
u Luc-sur-Mer.

6
00:03:01,544 --> 00:03:05,021
Mama je napravila vunene kupace
gace za mene i moga brata.

7
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:07,898
Imale su crvene pufne,

8
00:03:09,257 --> 00:03:10,536
kao tresnje.

9
00:03:11,375 --> 00:03:14,692
Nije samo nosenje ovih vocnih
ornamenata bilo apsurdno,

10
00:03:15,012 --> 00:03:17,969
vec se ni gace nikada nisu susile.

11
00:03:19,408 --> 00:03:20,926
Uvek smo bili u moru,

12
00:03:21,126 --> 00:03:23,884
tako da je vuna ostajala mokra
po celi dan,

13
00:03:24,083 --> 00:03:26,082
pesak se lepio na nase guzice,

14
00:03:26,521 --> 00:03:29,079
sto je moje prepone
strasno ranjavalo.

15
00:03:30,637 --> 00:03:31,676
Posle sedam dana,

16
00:03:31,876 --> 00:03:34,394
morao sam da hodam rasirenih nogu

17
00:03:34,594 --> 00:03:36,872
da ne bih vristao od bola.

18
00:03:38,071 --> 00:03:40,708
Besan sam na nasu majku
sto nas je terala da nosimo

19
00:03:40,908 --> 00:03:44,744
te gace cetiri godine za redom.

20
00:03:45,863 --> 00:03:48,741
Ali drago mi je
sto je nenamerno privukla

21
00:03:48,901 --> 00:03:51,858
moju paznju na moje genitalije.

22
00:03:52,497 --> 00:03:54,615
Tog leta, shvatio sam,

23
00:03:54,815 --> 00:03:57,213
da moram dobro brinuti
o svojim mudima.

24
00:04:13,398 --> 00:04:14,517
Idem u berbernicu.

25
00:04:14,717 --> 00:04:15,316
Opet?

26
00:04:18,074 --> 00:04:19,233
Bio sam tada star oko 12 godina.

27
00:04:19,912 --> 00:04:21,671
I voleo sam da odlazim u berbernicu.

28
00:04:26,546 --> 00:04:29,783
U nasem gradu bila je berbernica

29
00:04:30,023 --> 00:04:32,661
samo za muskarce,

30
00:04:32,860 --> 00:04:35,258
koju je vodila predivna zena iz Alzasa:

31
00:04:35,738 --> 00:04:37,376
divna Mrs. Sheaffer.

32
00:04:38,855 --> 00:04:40,094
Imala je malo musterija

33
00:04:41,652 --> 00:04:43,650
tako da niste morali da zakazujete.

34
00:04:43,930 --> 00:04:45,169
Nije imala muza,

35
00:04:45,809 --> 00:04:46,768
ali imala je mnogo ljubavnika.

36
00:04:48,486 --> 00:04:50,165
Obozavao sam da idem tamo.

37
00:04:58,637 --> 00:05:01,674
Kada bih otvorio vrata,
divan miris je

38
00:05:01,954 --> 00:05:03,952
milovao moje nozdrve, mesavina

39
00:05:04,152 --> 00:05:07,349
losiona, spreja za kosu,
ruzine vodice, sampona...

40
00:05:08,188 --> 00:05:09,627
Bio je opojan.

41
00:05:13,943 --> 00:05:16,500
Najlepsi od svih mirisa

42
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:19,418
bio je njen vlastiti.

43
00:05:20,697 --> 00:05:22,455
Imala je crvenu kosu

44
00:05:22,815 --> 00:05:25,532
i jako izrazen miris tela.

45
00:05:26,092 --> 00:05:27,890
To je bez sumnje smetalo
nekim musterijama,

46
00:05:28,090 --> 00:05:30,408
ali mene je izludjivalo.

47
00:05:32,126 --> 00:05:34,364
Izgledalo je kao da njeno
telo mirise na ljubav.

48
00:05:35,603 --> 00:05:36,762
Obozavao sam to.

49
00:05:41,557 --> 00:05:42,557
Sta da sisam?

50
00:05:42,756 --> 00:05:45,794
Moja majka voli da mi je kosa kratka.

51
00:05:50,869 --> 00:05:54,146
Prvo uzivanje je bilo pranje kose.

52
00:05:55,305 --> 00:05:57,543
Gospodja Shaeffer se naginjala
preko mene,

53
00:05:57,942 --> 00:06:00,300
njena dojka je
skoro dodirivala moje lice.

54
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:01,979
Duboko sam udisao,

55
00:06:02,179 --> 00:06:05,016
tiho, uranjao sam u njen miris.

56
00:06:07,414 --> 00:06:10,011
Nocu, u krevetu, jos uvek sam
mogao da osetim njen miris,

57
00:06:11,090 --> 00:06:14,927
i ceznuo da je uzmem u narucje.

58
00:06:15,846 --> 00:06:17,165
Skola dobro ide?

59
00:06:20,442 --> 00:06:21,801
Jesi li dobar ucenik?

60
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,479
Imas srece.

61
00:06:23,679 --> 00:06:26,157
Mrzela sam skolu.
Nisam volela disciplinu.

62
00:06:57,648 --> 00:07:00,245
Nisi zavrsio ukrstenicu.

63
00:07:02,883 --> 00:07:06,160
Oh da... hvala...
Zavrsicu kasnije.

64
00:07:09,757 --> 00:07:11,675
U junu 1947, pre raspusta,

65
00:07:11,955 --> 00:07:15,511
desilo se nesto
cega cu se uvek secati.

66
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:18,549
Bilo je jako toplo.

67
00:07:19,588 --> 00:07:21,146
Mirisala je bozanski.

68
00:08:06,265 --> 00:08:09,222
Te veceri video sam njenu tesku,

69
00:08:09,422 --> 00:08:11,740
idealno okruglu dojku,

70
00:08:12,579 --> 00:08:15,616
Bio sam toliko uznemiren
da nisam mogao da govorim.

71
00:08:18,574 --> 00:08:20,012
Jesi li dobro, Antoine?

72
00:08:20,212 --> 00:08:21,411
Dobro sam.

73
00:08:23,089 --> 00:08:24,129
cudno izgledas.

74
00:08:31,402 --> 00:08:32,801
Vecera je gotova!

75
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,158
Sta je binarni sistem?

76
00:08:36,597 --> 00:08:37,676
Ili postavimo to

77
00:08:37,876 --> 00:08:39,914
drugacije:

78
00:08:40,593 --> 00:08:43,830
Sta je to binarna macka?

79
00:08:44,949 --> 00:08:47,028
Ne znas, naravno.

80
00:08:47,227 --> 00:08:50,504
Ponovo,
moracu da te izbacim napolje!

81
00:08:51,543 --> 00:08:53,582
Normalna macka,

82
00:08:53,781 --> 00:08:55,899
je macka koja ima

83
00:08:56,099 --> 00:08:58,017
jednu glavu, dva oka

84
00:08:58,217 --> 00:08:59,736
i cetiri sape.

85
00:08:59,936 --> 00:09:02,054
Binarna macka,

86
00:09:02,413 --> 00:09:04,691
ima jednu glavu,

87
00:09:04,891 --> 00:09:06,610
jedno oko, jedno oko,

88
00:09:06,809 --> 00:09:08,848
jednu sapu, jednu sapu, jednu sapu

89
00:09:09,087 --> 00:09:10,766
i jednu sapu.

90
00:09:11,245 --> 00:09:12,684
Vidis li razliku?

91
00:09:13,883 --> 00:09:15,881
Mislio sam da ces to reci.

92
00:09:16,161 --> 00:09:17,520
On je video razliku!

93
00:09:17,719 --> 00:09:18,918
On je beznadezan!

94
00:09:19,398 --> 00:09:21,076
Sta bi ti zeleo da budes u zivotu?

95
00:09:21,276 --> 00:09:22,075
Civilni inzenjer.

96
00:09:22,315 --> 00:09:25,193
Zasto ne zongler po zici?

97
00:09:25,472 --> 00:09:27,191
Ostavi ga na miru, jos je mlad.

98
00:09:27,391 --> 00:09:28,589
Razocaran sam.

99
00:09:29,069 --> 00:09:31,866
Ako pocnes kao mali,
zavrsices kao mali.

100
00:09:34,824 --> 00:09:35,623
A ti?

101
00:09:36,023 --> 00:09:37,541
Sta ces ti raditi kasnije?

102
00:09:37,861 --> 00:09:40,658
Kasnije cu ozeniti frizerku.

103
00:09:48,172 --> 00:09:49,290
Zbog cega sam to uradio?

104
00:09:50,330 --> 00:09:52,048
Kazi mi zasto sam to uradio.

105
00:10:00,161 --> 00:10:02,518
Ja sam, mama. Otvori.

106
00:10:03,517 --> 00:10:04,996
Tvome ocu je zao.

107
00:10:05,516 --> 00:10:07,314
Zar ne vidis da je bio iznenadjen?

108
00:10:14,947 --> 00:10:15,826
Jesi li bolestan?

109
00:10:18,704 --> 00:10:19,743
Odgovori mi!

110
00:10:21,021 --> 00:10:21,901
Antoine?

111
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:23,819
Da li me cujes?

112
00:10:25,098 --> 00:10:26,257
Sta radis?

113
00:10:27,655 --> 00:10:28,574
Jesi li u redu?

114
00:10:30,932 --> 00:10:31,772
Pa?

115
00:10:32,011 --> 00:10:33,490
On ne odgovara.

116
00:10:34,169 --> 00:10:35,368
Mozda je pao u nesvest!

117
00:10:35,688 --> 00:10:37,566
Od samara?

118
00:10:38,366 --> 00:10:41,003
Brinem se!
Moracemo da razvalimo vrata!

119
00:10:41,243 --> 00:10:43,441
Smiri se!
Ja cu razgovarati sa njim.

120
00:10:46,318 --> 00:10:49,755
Antoine, tata je. Izvinjavam se.

121
00:10:49,995 --> 00:10:51,394
Zao mi je zbog onoga sto sam ucinio.

122
00:10:51,633 --> 00:10:53,112
Radi u zivotu ono sto zelis.

123
00:10:54,151 --> 00:10:57,548
Ostao sam tamo citav sat,
zureci u plafon.

124
00:10:58,547 --> 00:11:01,105
Gospodja Shaeffer je vec bila moja.

125
00:11:01,704 --> 00:11:04,142
Njeno telo, njen miris su bili moji.

126
00:11:05,341 --> 00:11:06,300
Pobedio sam:

127
00:11:07,099 --> 00:11:09,057
Bicu frizerkin muz.

128
00:12:03,767 --> 00:12:05,206
Sprema se oluja.

129
00:12:05,805 --> 00:12:07,124
Mozda.

130
00:12:16,036 --> 00:12:17,515
Dobar dan, Mr. Morvoisieux.

131
00:12:20,352 --> 00:12:22,670
Ako plasticno cvece raste u basti,

132
00:12:23,070 --> 00:12:24,428
bice to dokaz...

133
00:12:24,628 --> 00:12:25,947
A miris?

134
00:12:26,147 --> 00:12:27,346
Zasmejavas me,

135
00:12:27,825 --> 00:12:31,582
znas da nista ne postoji bez modela.

136
00:12:32,581 --> 00:12:34,179
Plasticno cvece je OK,

137
00:12:34,459 --> 00:12:37,376
ali prvo je moralo postojati pravo,

138
00:12:37,576 --> 00:12:39,854
inace nebi moglo da
postoji ni vestacko!

139
00:12:40,334 --> 00:12:41,133
Mrvice kafe?

140
00:12:42,412 --> 00:12:44,010
Sta je sa njima?

141
00:12:44,290 --> 00:12:45,449
One postoje, zar ne?

142
00:12:45,729 --> 00:12:47,088
Da, nastavi...

143
00:12:47,287 --> 00:12:48,806
One ne rastu na drvetu,

144
00:12:49,086 --> 00:12:50,325
ne postoje u prirodi,

145
00:12:50,604 --> 00:12:52,643
ali mi ih koristimo.

146
00:12:52,922 --> 00:12:54,880
Dakle mogu se napraviti mrvice

147
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:55,760
bez uzora.

148
00:12:55,959 --> 00:12:57,518
Mi govorimo o Bogu!

149
00:12:57,718 --> 00:12:58,797
Bog!

150
00:12:59,436 --> 00:13:02,553
Kako smo, do vraga dosli
do mrvica kafe?

151
00:13:03,553 --> 00:13:05,151
Kako prevarantsko rezonovanje!

152
00:13:09,147 --> 00:13:12,065
Ti tako kazes!
Uvek zelis da budes u pravu!

153
00:13:12,344 --> 00:13:15,741
Mrvice kafe su samo primer.

154
00:13:16,461 --> 00:13:19,378
Bog je beskonacan.
Njega ne mozes dokuciti.

155
00:13:19,578 --> 00:13:20,697
Ista stvar.

156
00:13:20,897 --> 00:13:22,455
Bog postoji.

157
00:13:23,254 --> 00:13:25,173
Tako ti kazes, ali...

158
00:13:35,323 --> 00:13:36,762
On je kasno stigao.

159
00:13:41,078 --> 00:13:43,076
To je samo njegova zguzvana jakna.

160
00:13:44,995 --> 00:13:47,432
Pre je pazio da to izbegne.

161
00:13:50,709 --> 00:13:52,268
U pravu si. On stari.

162
00:15:11,835 --> 00:15:15,152
Pre 10 godina, Mathilda je radila
u Isidorovoj berberskoj radnji.

163
00:15:15,831 --> 00:15:19,188
Njen sef, Isidore Agopian,
imalo je 3 zenska frizera.

164
00:15:19,388 --> 00:15:20,627
Bilo je homoseksualac.

165
00:15:20,827 --> 00:15:23,344
Mrzeo je da sisa zensku kosu.

166
00:15:27,621 --> 00:15:29,858
Mathilde mu je bila omiljena.

167
00:15:30,058 --> 00:15:33,735
Njen takt, njen sarm,
trunka sete,

168
00:15:34,254 --> 00:15:35,773
ali i beskrajno graciozan stav,

169
00:15:35,973 --> 00:15:37,691
ocaravali su klijentelu.

170
00:15:38,451 --> 00:15:43,046
Kada se gospodin Isidore
penzionisao u 60 - tim

171
00:15:43,646 --> 00:15:45,564
ponudio je radnju Mathildi.

172
00:15:45,924 --> 00:15:46,803
Za mene?

173
00:15:48,122 --> 00:15:49,321
Ja nemam novaca!

174
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:51,439
To je u redu,
nisu mi potrebni sada.

175
00:15:51,639 --> 00:15:55,435
Otplacuj po malo, svaki mesec,
dok ja ne umrem.Kao kiriju.

176
00:15:55,635 --> 00:15:58,232
Voleo bih da znam da je
radnja u tvojim rukama.

177
00:15:58,432 --> 00:16:00,111
Ti si od one vrste kojoj verujem.

178
00:16:00,311 --> 00:16:01,350
Kazi da.

179
00:16:06,425 --> 00:16:07,104
Mathilda je

180
00:16:07,664 --> 00:16:08,703
pristala.

181
00:16:10,421 --> 00:16:13,419
Morala se osloboditi
preostale dve radnice,

182
00:16:13,618 --> 00:16:14,737
koje su bile ljubomorne.

183
00:16:15,537 --> 00:16:18,014
Posto je volela samocu,
radnju je vodila sama.

184
00:16:18,214 --> 00:16:20,452
Bila je prevelika za nju,
ali, pa sta?

185
00:16:22,171 --> 00:16:23,489
Tada sam je sreo.

186
00:16:54,101 --> 00:16:55,500
Mozete li me primiti?

187
00:16:56,219 --> 00:16:58,537
Zao mi je, cekam nekoga.

188
00:16:59,416 --> 00:17:00,655
Oprostite, molim vas,

189
00:17:01,614 --> 00:17:03,373
Vidim da moram da zakazem.

190
00:17:04,412 --> 00:17:06,250
Vratite se za pola sata.

191
00:17:06,570 --> 00:17:08,408
Imate li neki posao koji
treba da uradite?

192
00:17:08,608 --> 00:17:10,886
Da... dobro... Odlicno.

193
00:17:13,923 --> 00:17:15,162
Zelite li moje ime?

194
00:17:16,081 --> 00:17:16,880
Ne brinite se.

195
00:17:21,876 --> 00:17:23,554
Pretesko? Odustajes li?

196
00:17:24,074 --> 00:17:25,872
Nikada ne odustajem!

197
00:17:26,072 --> 00:17:28,989
Zapamti, ukrstene reci su kao zene:

198
00:17:29,189 --> 00:17:31,907
Otpor cini pobedu sladjom.

199
00:17:32,106 --> 00:17:33,545
Znam o cemu govorim.

200
00:17:33,745 --> 00:17:36,502
Videces kasnije da sam upravu.

201
00:17:37,022 --> 00:17:39,020
Kasnije,
kada ja popunim ukrstenicu?

202
00:17:39,220 --> 00:17:41,218
Vremenom.

203
00:17:41,618 --> 00:17:43,816
Ponavljaj ovo:
Sto se vise opiru...

204
00:17:44,375 --> 00:17:46,254
pobeda je sladja.

205
00:17:47,492 --> 00:17:49,650
Dobro. Idi sada i igraj se.

206
00:17:49,890 --> 00:17:52,408
Podigni gace,
sakrij testise.

207
00:18:02,519 --> 00:18:03,797
Niko nije dosao.

208
00:18:05,636 --> 00:18:06,995
Kasnije, Mathilda...

209
00:18:07,394 --> 00:18:10,112
Tada nisam znao da joj je
ime Mathilda

210
00:18:10,311 --> 00:18:11,950
...nikada nije ni rec prozborila

211
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:14,188
o njenom fantomskom klijentu.

212
00:18:14,907 --> 00:18:17,825
Nije li to bio njen nesvesni mamac?

213
00:18:18,024 --> 00:18:19,503
Nikada necu znati.

214
00:18:20,582 --> 00:18:24,259
Ali bio sam unisten:
u jednoj sekundi moga zivota,

215
00:18:24,459 --> 00:18:26,017
nakon tako duge potrage,

216
00:18:26,776 --> 00:18:28,255
voleo sam frizerku.

217
00:18:30,493 --> 00:18:33,650
Nakon 25 minuta, predao
sam se i dosao sam zeni

218
00:18:33,850 --> 00:18:36,727
sa kojom cu, znao sam,
provesti ostatak ziovota.

219
00:18:38,246 --> 00:18:38,965
Dobar dan, ponovo.

220
00:18:43,241 --> 00:18:46,358
Uvek sam lose pocinjao: Previse
sam nervozan da bih cutao.

221
00:18:46,558 --> 00:18:49,156
U prodavnici cipela, rekao sam
"Voleo bih neke cipele..."

222
00:18:49,356 --> 00:18:50,874
Danas sam trazio sisanje.

223
00:18:51,074 --> 00:18:52,273
Ovo je za sisanje.

224
00:18:57,908 --> 00:18:58,947
Da li vi to razdvajate?

225
00:18:59,267 --> 00:19:02,304
Ja... da... ako zelite...

226
00:19:03,223 --> 00:19:04,462
Kako zelite.

227
00:19:05,941 --> 00:19:09,058
U redu. Ali da nije preostro.

228
00:19:09,377 --> 00:19:10,456
Ne brinite.

229
00:19:29,039 --> 00:19:30,238
Imate cuperak.

230
00:19:31,677 --> 00:19:33,555
Znam. Oduvek sam ga imao.

231
00:19:34,434 --> 00:19:36,113
Vasa kosa je sisana prekratko.

232
00:19:36,872 --> 00:19:39,310
cesto sam isao kod frizera.
Volim to.

233
00:19:39,710 --> 00:19:41,308
Zaista? Zasto?

234
00:19:42,587 --> 00:19:43,626
Ne znam.

235
00:19:51,858 --> 00:19:53,257
Naravno,

236
00:19:53,857 --> 00:19:56,214
pitao sam se da li  Mathilda

237
00:19:56,494 --> 00:19:57,533
nosi grudnjak.

238
00:19:58,572 --> 00:20:00,770
Ubrzo sam bio siguran
da ga ne nosi.

239
00:20:13,439 --> 00:20:14,718
Zamisljao sam...

240
00:20:14,917 --> 00:20:18,474
...njene bradavice
koje se trljaju o njenu bluzu,

241
00:20:19,113 --> 00:20:21,911
i, nadrazene, dodiruju moj vrat.

242
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:24,868
Te grudi ce uskoro biti moje.

243
00:20:25,348 --> 00:20:27,306
Vec sam zeleo da ih pomilujem.

244
00:21:14,782 --> 00:21:18,499
Autopsija je kod gospodje Sheaffer,
pokazala ogromnu dozu barbiturata

245
00:21:19,858 --> 00:21:21,736
Bez oporuke, bez pisma,

246
00:21:21,936 --> 00:21:23,335
brza sahrana,

247
00:21:23,854 --> 00:21:26,052
kojoj, naravno,
nisam mogao prisustvovati.

248
00:21:27,211 --> 00:21:30,648
Otada, ja nikada nisam mogao
prestati da mislim na nju,

249
00:21:31,967 --> 00:21:34,604
I zarko sam voleo zenske grudi.

250
00:22:02,779 --> 00:22:04,177
Hocete li se udati za mene?

251
00:22:27,396 --> 00:22:28,315
35 franaka.

252
00:22:38,106 --> 00:22:39,105
Oprostite mi.

253
00:22:45,499 --> 00:22:48,976
Secam se te besane noci ispod
Mathildinog prozora.

254
00:22:52,173 --> 00:22:55,690
Zeleo sam da ona,
zbaci pokrivac,

255
00:22:56,289 --> 00:22:59,487
da ustane po casu vode,
i da se, gledajuci se u ogledalu,

256
00:22:59,686 --> 00:23:02,524
razodene
pre nego sto se vrati u krevet...

257
00:23:03,043 --> 00:23:04,362
...misleci na mene.

258
00:23:05,561 --> 00:23:08,279
U stvari, ona je mozda zvucala
kao da spava.

259
00:23:08,478 --> 00:23:10,556
Mozda me je zaboravila.

260
00:23:10,836 --> 00:23:13,114
Zasto sam mislio
da je sama u krevetu?

261
00:23:13,634 --> 00:23:15,192
Nisam je poznavao.

262
00:23:53,277 --> 00:23:53,957
Moj otac,

263
00:23:54,236 --> 00:23:55,715
je govorio da je zivot jednostavan,

264
00:23:56,754 --> 00:24:00,311
i da ces, samo ako to jako zelis,

265
00:24:00,511 --> 00:24:01,270
to i dobiti.

266
00:24:02,469 --> 00:24:03,708
Neuspeh je bio dokaz,

267
00:24:03,987 --> 00:24:06,145
da zelja nije bila dovoljno jaka.

268
00:25:00,855 --> 00:25:02,654
Ni jedan san nije nemoguc.

269
00:25:03,333 --> 00:25:05,851
Zeleo sam Mathildu
vise nego bilo sta drugo.

270
00:25:06,051 --> 00:25:08,968
Bila je kao bujica:
srusila bi i tvrdjavu.

271
00:25:09,168 --> 00:25:11,246
Ucinio sam je svojom zauvek.

272
00:25:13,444 --> 00:25:15,642
3 nedelje kasnije,
vratio sam se u radnju,

273
00:25:15,842 --> 00:25:18,879
jedva da sam bio nervozan,
samo uzasno uzbudjen.

274
00:25:19,438 --> 00:25:21,636
Moja kosa nije imala vremena
da poraste

275
00:25:21,836 --> 00:25:24,793
dovoljno za pravo sisanje.

276
00:25:35,464 --> 00:25:38,781
Mathilda se pretvarala da me
nikada u zivotu nije videla...

277
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,579
Tiha i udaljena.

278
00:25:40,939 --> 00:25:43,736
To je ucinilo
da je zelim vise nego ikada.

279
00:25:44,415 --> 00:25:46,054
Ona je to verovatno znala.

280
00:25:47,692 --> 00:25:50,810
Zamisli, on nikada u zivotu
nije bio u berbernici!

281
00:25:51,129 --> 00:25:51,849
Kada bi njegova kosa

282
00:25:52,128 --> 00:25:54,446
pokrila vrat,
sam bi je odsecao...

283
00:25:55,365 --> 00:25:58,523
Nije mu trebalo ogledalo.
Radio je to po osecaju.

284
00:25:58,882 --> 00:25:59,602
Radio je to dobro.

285
00:26:02,479 --> 00:26:04,877
Sve sa masinicom,
"kao da sisa travnjak".

286
00:26:05,396 --> 00:26:08,234
Jos uvek ga mogu cuti. Kakav lik!

287
00:26:10,312 --> 00:26:11,271
Oni ga vise ne cine...

288
00:26:11,551 --> 00:26:12,869
da lici na sebe.

289
00:26:14,908 --> 00:26:15,867
Gotovo.

290
00:26:16,106 --> 00:26:17,785
Ovaj put je bilo brze.

291
00:26:17,985 --> 00:26:20,902
Nisam pravila frizuru,
prerano je.

292
00:26:21,222 --> 00:26:22,700
Ucinicemo to sledeci put.

293
00:26:35,209 --> 00:26:36,568
Hocu li ostati tako nasusuren?

294
00:26:36,768 --> 00:26:37,527
Naravno, zasto da ne?

295
00:26:37,886 --> 00:26:40,764
Gospodin Agopian me je naucio
da spavam na ledjima.

296
00:26:40,964 --> 00:26:42,402
Neka vas to ne uznemirava.

297
00:26:42,602 --> 00:26:44,840
Dodjite u subotu,
pocesljacu vam je.

298
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:46,039
To je lepo od vas.

299
00:26:47,198 --> 00:26:48,117
Do subote.

300
00:27:47,223 --> 00:27:49,101
Sta ti je bilo onoga dana?

301
00:27:49,301 --> 00:27:51,939
Verovatno si se salio samnom, ali...

302
00:27:53,098 --> 00:27:55,495
ako se nisi zavitlavao,

303
00:27:55,695 --> 00:27:57,893
onda ja prihvatam tvoju ponudu.

304
00:27:58,972 --> 00:28:00,731
Ako jos uvek vazi,

305
00:28:01,090 --> 00:28:01,969
da,

306
00:28:03,048 --> 00:28:04,327
udacu se za tebe.

307
00:28:10,442 --> 00:28:11,880
Zovem se Mathilda.

308
00:28:21,072 --> 00:28:24,389
Prvi put kada sam usao ovamo,
pitao sam mozes li me primiti.

309
00:28:24,589 --> 00:28:25,868
Rekla si ne,

310
00:28:26,067 --> 00:28:28,425
ali u stvari si me vec primila.

311
00:28:28,665 --> 00:28:29,824
Secam se.

312
00:28:30,024 --> 00:28:32,501
I pitao sam, treba li da
ti kazem moje ime.

313
00:28:32,701 --> 00:28:34,580
Opet si rekla ne.

314
00:28:35,379 --> 00:28:37,497
Sve dok me jednostavno
nisi pustila da ti ga kazem.

315
00:28:38,096 --> 00:28:39,775
Zacudo, ovi susreti...

316
00:28:41,733 --> 00:28:43,651
Imas jake misice u butinama.

317
00:28:43,851 --> 00:28:47,208
Igrala sam fudbal u skoli -
Bila sam desni bek.

318
00:28:48,807 --> 00:28:51,324
- Znas li fudbal?
- Naravno. Tu je lopta...

319
00:28:51,644 --> 00:28:54,841
Ne smes koristiti ruke,
i to je timska igra...

320
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,878
Vidim da si ekspert.

321
00:28:58,478 --> 00:29:01,875
Sport me odbija. Kao i putovanje.

322
00:29:03,113 --> 00:29:04,952
Ni ja ne volim nigde da idem.

323
00:29:05,152 --> 00:29:06,231
To je dobro.

324
00:29:06,590 --> 00:29:10,067
Dogovoreno je: ostacemo ovde.
Bice to divno.

325
00:29:11,666 --> 00:29:12,465
I ja mislim tako.

326
00:29:15,142 --> 00:29:18,499
Ja cu se baviti porudzbinama,
pismima i tako to.

327
00:29:18,699 --> 00:29:19,778
Volim tvoje ruke.

328
00:29:21,137 --> 00:29:23,535
Primetila sam ih jednom.
Divno!

329
00:29:24,774 --> 00:29:28,650
Imas oziljak tamo,
kao polumesec.

330
00:29:28,850 --> 00:29:29,969
Pao sam sa bicikla.

331
00:29:30,169 --> 00:29:31,807
I ti vozis bicikl?

332
00:29:32,007 --> 00:29:34,445
Vise ne.

333
00:29:34,844 --> 00:29:35,843
Proslost je mrtva.

334
00:29:36,043 --> 00:29:37,082
Apsolutno.

335
00:29:39,360 --> 00:29:42,597
Stanovi su gore.
Malo je, ali...

336
00:29:45,035 --> 00:29:46,474
Zelis li da vidis?

337
00:29:48,072 --> 00:29:49,431
Zovem se Antoine.

338
00:29:52,668 --> 00:29:56,225
Kada sam rekao da cu ozeniti
frizerku, tata je umro

339
00:29:56,505 --> 00:29:57,623
od srcanog udara.

340
00:29:57,823 --> 00:30:01,220
Iz lojalnosti, mama je odbila
da upozna Mathildu

341
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:02,899
ili da vidi radnju.

342
00:30:03,098 --> 00:30:03,778
Mathilda

343
00:30:04,058 --> 00:30:04,937
nije imala porodicu.

344
00:30:05,137 --> 00:30:06,495
Hej, ti si veliki drkadzija...

345
00:30:06,975 --> 00:30:08,014
nisi ni otvorio moj poklon.

346
00:30:13,849 --> 00:30:14,968
To je iznenadjenje?

347
00:30:15,207 --> 00:30:16,486
Iznenadjenje?

348
00:30:16,726 --> 00:30:18,564
To ce te svakako iznenaditi.

349
00:30:18,764 --> 00:30:19,723
Uplasio si me.

350
00:30:19,963 --> 00:30:22,481
Bili smo sa mojim bratom,
njegovom zenom,

351
00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:23,879
i gospodinom Agopianom.

352
00:30:24,079 --> 00:30:25,918
U najmanju ruku bilo je intimno.

353
00:30:29,634 --> 00:30:31,992
Insistiram da to obuces.
Prepoznajes li to?

354
00:30:32,232 --> 00:30:34,350
Kako bih mogao zaboraviti?

355
00:30:34,749 --> 00:30:37,267
Obicno su bile prevelike,
nisu pasovale kao rukavica,

356
00:30:37,467 --> 00:30:38,426
Pricaj.

357
00:30:38,986 --> 00:30:39,865
Nosi ih veceras.

358
00:30:40,065 --> 00:30:41,423
Izvadi ...

359
00:30:42,023 --> 00:30:43,901
Jako cudno, dopada mi se.

360
00:30:44,341 --> 00:30:45,380
Volim pufne.

361
00:30:45,620 --> 00:30:47,618
To su tresnje, ne pufne.

362
00:30:49,336 --> 00:30:50,775
Otegnu se kada su mokre.

363
00:30:51,534 --> 00:30:53,093
Znas, pletena vuna...

364
00:30:53,572 --> 00:30:55,371
Obuci ih, za stara vremena,
za ime boga.

365
00:30:55,570 --> 00:30:57,609
Pitam se
da li ti jos uvek odgovaraju.

366
00:31:03,843 --> 00:31:04,722
Evo...

367
00:31:05,202 --> 00:31:07,000
To je od tvoje majke.

368
00:31:12,555 --> 00:31:13,514
Koliko ste bili stari?

369
00:31:13,754 --> 00:31:14,633
12.

370
00:31:14,833 --> 00:31:15,392
cudno...

371
00:31:16,551 --> 00:31:20,148
Kao da su pravljene po tvojoj meri.

372
00:31:20,907 --> 00:31:22,865
- Izgledas kao saljivdzina.
- Bio sam.

373
00:31:23,984 --> 00:31:25,783
Mogu li da vidim tvoje slike iz detinjstva?

374
00:31:27,022 --> 00:31:28,460
Nisam sacuvala ni jednu.

375
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:29,939
To me uznemiruje.

376
00:31:30,139 --> 00:31:31,458
Zasto?

377
00:31:31,657 --> 00:31:32,856
Vreme jako brzo leti.

378
00:31:33,536 --> 00:31:34,575
Pogresno ime,

379
00:31:34,854 --> 00:31:36,173
moze unistiti proizvod.

380
00:31:36,373 --> 00:31:37,652
Pa kako onda lik

381
00:31:37,932 --> 00:31:40,649
po imenu Givenchy

382
00:31:40,889 --> 00:31:42,208
prodaje toliko parfema?

383
00:31:44,566 --> 00:31:47,843
Priznacu nesto:
Moje pravo ime je Dupre...

384
00:31:49,361 --> 00:31:50,400
Ambroise Dupre.

385
00:31:51,479 --> 00:31:52,438
A Agopian?

386
00:31:52,878 --> 00:31:54,916
Egzotika, moj prijatelju...

387
00:31:55,156 --> 00:31:57,194
Jermensko, znaci orientalno.

388
00:31:57,394 --> 00:31:59,272
Orijentalni frizer znaci klasu...

389
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:01,670
Izvinite...

390
00:32:02,789 --> 00:32:04,108
Mislio sam da je otvoreno.

391
00:32:05,027 --> 00:32:06,745
Zaboravila sam da zakljucam vrata.

392
00:32:06,985 --> 00:32:08,304
Osim toga, nedelja je.

393
00:32:09,023 --> 00:32:10,422
Tako je!

394
00:32:11,141 --> 00:32:11,861
Ja sam budala!

395
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:13,779
Idem.

396
00:32:14,218 --> 00:32:16,656
Imamo neki sampanjac.

397
00:32:17,575 --> 00:32:20,692
Ne zelim da vas uznemiravam...
Vi cete se vencati.

398
00:32:21,092 --> 00:32:23,050
Ne smetate nam.

399
00:32:25,568 --> 00:32:27,606
Da... Smetam!

400
00:32:28,365 --> 00:32:29,844
Ovo je porodicni skup...

401
00:32:30,763 --> 00:32:32,482
Kada ste skoro porodica...

402
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:35,599
Zbog cega ste dosli?

403
00:32:36,918 --> 00:32:37,597
Zbog moje brade...

404
00:32:38,196 --> 00:32:39,355
Zelim da je odsecem.

405
00:32:39,595 --> 00:32:40,235
Skroz?

406
00:32:41,154 --> 00:32:43,312
Ljudi kazu da me cini
da izgledam tuzan,

407
00:32:43,631 --> 00:32:46,029
tako da, posto sam prolazio,
resio sam...

408
00:32:46,269 --> 00:32:48,987
Sedite, trajace samo 5 minuta.

409
00:33:36,583 --> 00:33:37,502
Steta.

410
00:33:42,817 --> 00:33:43,976
Zao mi je.

411
00:33:45,974 --> 00:33:47,573
Ne, ne danas.

412
00:33:54,606 --> 00:33:55,685
Sve najbolje...

413
00:35:12,895 --> 00:35:14,653
Mathilda je bila moj zivot.

414
00:35:15,412 --> 00:35:18,490
Znao sam da kada oni odu,
i kada se vrata zatvore,

415
00:35:18,689 --> 00:35:21,966
sve ce biti postavljeno zauvek,
za nas oboje.

416
00:35:23,525 --> 00:35:25,603
Radnja ce se zatvoriti oko nas.

417
00:35:25,963 --> 00:35:27,641
Bicemo tako cvrsto spojeni

418
00:35:27,841 --> 00:35:30,838
da se nista hladno ili zlo,
nece uvuci izmedju nas,

419
00:35:31,038 --> 00:35:33,276
nista grubo ili hladno...

420
00:35:33,636 --> 00:35:34,635
nikada...

421
00:35:48,662 --> 00:35:50,021
Stigli smo u Luc-sur-Mer

422
00:35:50,220 --> 00:35:54,217
tako da je Mathilda mogla videti
gde sam ja nosio vunene gace.

423
00:35:55,895 --> 00:35:58,093
Kratki medeni mesec:
bili smo u zurbi

424
00:35:58,293 --> 00:36:02,050
da pocnemo nas stvarni zivot u
nasoj nepokretnoj luksuznoj krstarici.

425
00:36:36,338 --> 00:36:37,217
cekaj...

426
00:36:38,376 --> 00:36:39,335
Sedi.

427
00:36:43,891 --> 00:36:46,689
Malo skratiti. Ne previse.

428
00:36:47,048 --> 00:36:48,807
Ispravite se malo.

429
00:37:10,004 --> 00:37:11,163
Izvinite, gospodjo,

430
00:37:11,683 --> 00:37:12,722
ne sisamo zene.

431
00:37:13,161 --> 00:37:14,240
Znam.

432
00:37:21,210 --> 00:37:21,889
Izvinite me.

433
00:37:29,797 --> 00:37:32,435
Sam si trazio! Evo!

434
00:37:38,269 --> 00:37:41,307
Narode, izvinjavam se zbog ovoga.
Oni mora da su sokirani

435
00:37:41,507 --> 00:37:42,785
tvojim ponasanjem.

436
00:37:43,145 --> 00:37:44,464
Oni ne znaju tvoje.

437
00:37:44,863 --> 00:37:46,222
Sumnjam da im je stalo do toga.

438
00:37:48,220 --> 00:37:50,259
Ovo je moja zena,

439
00:37:50,658 --> 00:37:51,977
Germaine Gora.

440
00:37:52,976 --> 00:37:54,854
Ja sam Julien Gora.

441
00:38:12,638 --> 00:38:15,316
Vidite kako je to bilo uredno?
Na dugme!

442
00:38:16,634 --> 00:38:18,033
Ona je zadivljujuca!

443
00:38:18,872 --> 00:38:22,029
Igrala je ping - pong.
Jos uvek imamo pehare.

444
00:38:22,309 --> 00:38:23,988
Klupske trofeje.

445
00:38:24,227 --> 00:38:27,225
Zaboravi sisanje.Nema smisla.

446
00:38:30,582 --> 00:38:32,020
Onda malo losiona?

447
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:34,738
Ako zelite... losion je u redu.

448
00:38:35,457 --> 00:38:38,654
Prestala je da igra zbog dece.
Troje!

449
00:38:39,853 --> 00:38:41,212
Podizati ih, to je posao.

450
00:38:41,811 --> 00:38:43,769
Skidam kapu zbog toga.

451
00:38:44,649 --> 00:38:47,766
Ali ona nije obicna domacica,
koja mlatara metlom.

452
00:38:48,285 --> 00:38:51,802
Primetili ste njenu odecu,
njenu sminku.

453
00:38:55,199 --> 00:38:56,838
Sta mislite o njoj?

454
00:38:57,317 --> 00:38:59,235
Lepa je, veoma lepa.

455
00:39:02,073 --> 00:39:03,392
A vi, gospodine?

456
00:39:03,591 --> 00:39:06,469
Vazno je cuti musko misljenje.

457
00:39:07,468 --> 00:39:09,546
Ono sto sam video, bilo je divno.

458
00:39:10,105 --> 00:39:11,664
Slazem se sa vama.

459
00:39:12,143 --> 00:39:15,061
Ona je velicanstvena zena!

460
00:39:15,820 --> 00:39:17,938
Videste li te oci?

461
00:39:18,178 --> 00:39:20,256
cak su i lepse, kada je  besna.

462
00:39:20,456 --> 00:39:21,135
Da, naravno.

463
00:39:23,093 --> 00:39:25,411
Zaista jedna izuzetna zena!

464
00:39:29,927 --> 00:39:32,725
Zdravo. Izvinite nas.

465
00:39:33,284 --> 00:39:35,562
Hvala na svemu.
Sta sam duzan?

466
00:39:35,762 --> 00:39:37,081
Nista.

467
00:39:49,549 --> 00:39:51,867
"Izgubiti 5 kilograma za dve nedelje

468
00:39:52,067 --> 00:39:55,504
"ne jeduci nista
osim krastavce i caj..."

469
00:39:56,583 --> 00:39:57,742
Verujes li to?

470
00:39:58,661 --> 00:40:00,579
- Gde si to procitala?
- U ovome.

471
00:40:00,939 --> 00:40:03,616
Oni kazu da je zdravstveno sigurno.

472
00:40:04,535 --> 00:40:05,774
Koliko je sati?

473
00:40:07,812 --> 00:40:09,051
15 minuta do 7.

474
00:40:11,129 --> 00:40:12,168
Hajde da zatvorimo.

475
00:40:42,900 --> 00:40:46,297
Izgubi samo pola kila,
i ja cu sesti na autobus...

476
00:40:51,692 --> 00:40:54,250
Onda mi obecaj nesto,
samo jednu stvar:

477
00:40:55,249 --> 00:40:57,367
onoga dana kada me
vise ne budes voleo

478
00:40:57,567 --> 00:40:59,205
nemoj se pretvarati da me volis.

479
00:41:11,314 --> 00:41:12,353
Musterija!

480
00:41:14,152 --> 00:41:15,830
Bice on sutrasnja musterija.

481
00:41:38,370 --> 00:41:39,329
Prestani sa tim!

482
00:41:39,888 --> 00:41:41,007
Kakva dosada!

483
00:41:46,602 --> 00:41:47,961
Prestani sa time, Edwarde!

484
00:41:48,240 --> 00:41:49,879
Znas da si obecao!

485
00:41:50,718 --> 00:41:53,596
Seti se sta je tata rekao.
Edwarde, to ce se uraditi!

486
00:41:53,795 --> 00:41:55,434
Gledaj ove lepe knjige.

487
00:41:55,634 --> 00:41:58,831
Evo u jednoj su brodovi,
i konji.

488
00:41:59,071 --> 00:42:00,789
Gledaj, da li volis konje?

489
00:42:01,229 --> 00:42:03,946
Gledaj kako je lepa dama
koja ti je dala knjige.

490
00:42:04,146 --> 00:42:07,023
I ti si lep, Edwarde,
Veoma lep, sada.

491
00:42:07,263 --> 00:42:09,821
Imate li neke puske?

492
00:42:10,021 --> 00:42:11,819
One sto pucaju i izbacuju varnice?

493
00:42:12,059 --> 00:42:14,576
- Imam lokomotivu.
- To ga nece interesovati.

494
00:42:14,776 --> 00:42:18,453
Gledaj, evo stolica za tebe,
sa jastucetom.

495
00:42:19,052 --> 00:42:21,610
Kako lepo jastuce.

496
00:42:25,047 --> 00:42:26,006
On cak ni nije nas.

497
00:42:26,525 --> 00:42:28,404
Usvojili smo ga. Grozna greska!

498
00:42:28,923 --> 00:42:30,242
Imate li vi dece?

499
00:42:30,482 --> 00:42:32,600
Pametno!
Nikada ne usvajajte ni jedno!

500
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:34,878
Oni ce vas unistiti.

501
00:42:35,197 --> 00:42:36,676
Zaglavicete se sa njima.

502
00:42:36,916 --> 00:42:38,714
Budi dobar, Edwarde.
Imam slatkis.

503
00:42:39,793 --> 00:42:41,672
Treba nam konopac,
da ga privezemo za stolicu.

504
00:42:41,991 --> 00:42:43,550
Ja cu mu drzati glavu,
a vi ga osisajte...

505
00:42:43,909 --> 00:42:45,108
On ce se smiriti...

506
00:42:45,348 --> 00:42:47,706
Pokazacu ti nesto

507
00:42:47,946 --> 00:42:49,265
sto nikada nisi video.

508
00:44:32,610 --> 00:44:33,849
Mi nemamo dece.

509
00:44:34,049 --> 00:44:37,126
Mi imamo druge ljude:
Edwarda, Paula, Andrewa,

510
00:44:37,326 --> 00:44:39,164
Armanda, Jeremya, Etiennea, Simona.

511
00:44:39,524 --> 00:44:42,041
Neki sigurno cvikaju od pranja kose.

512
00:44:43,280 --> 00:44:45,598
Kratka kosa za pricesca i odmore

513
00:44:45,798 --> 00:44:48,475
ne previse ogoljen vrat, tokom zime.

514
00:44:49,315 --> 00:44:51,872
A Mathilde je cuvala
svoj stomacic ravnim,

515
00:44:52,192 --> 00:44:55,669
Glatki stomacic, koji trudnoca
nikada nece deformisati.

516
00:44:56,668 --> 00:44:57,587
Nismo imali prijatelje.

517
00:44:58,946 --> 00:45:00,504
Nikada ih necemo ni imati.

518
00:45:01,304 --> 00:45:03,342
Sta bi oni mogli dodati
nasim zivotima?

519
00:45:03,941 --> 00:45:06,259
Osudjivao sam parove

520
00:45:06,459 --> 00:45:09,096
koji su izlazili sa drugim parovima,

521
00:45:09,376 --> 00:45:10,415
isli zajedno na odmore...

522
00:45:12,493 --> 00:45:14,611
To je bio dokaz da tu nema ljubavi,

523
00:45:14,891 --> 00:45:18,568
ambis, premoscen
vanjskim prijateljstvima.

524
00:45:19,727 --> 00:45:21,605
Dobro nam je, Mathilda.

525
00:45:22,324 --> 00:45:25,362
Srecni smo zajedno,
to je sve sto je bitno.

526
00:45:31,956 --> 00:45:32,995
Gotovo je.

527
00:45:33,674 --> 00:45:35,552
Vidis, nije bilo tako strasno...

528
00:45:47,182 --> 00:45:48,820
cistiji je svakako.

529
00:45:49,020 --> 00:45:52,057
Zapamtite sta sam vam rekla:
nikada ne usvajajte.

530
00:45:52,257 --> 00:45:53,576
Ne brinite...

531
00:46:11,559 --> 00:46:12,838
Svidja li ti se ova?

532
00:46:14,197 --> 00:46:15,995
Juce sam je kupio.

533
00:46:16,195 --> 00:46:17,234
Veoma je lepa.

534
00:46:19,232 --> 00:46:20,111
Plesi sa mnom...

535
00:46:22,509 --> 00:46:24,747
Ne znam kako da
plesem uz ovu muziku.

536
00:46:26,466 --> 00:46:27,145
Ni ja.

537
00:46:27,425 --> 00:46:31,021
Pa? Zatvori oci,
i reci sebi da te niko ne gleda.

538
00:46:31,221 --> 00:46:32,220
Hajde...

539
00:46:43,690 --> 00:46:45,009
Vidis kako je lako?

540
00:46:55,839 --> 00:46:56,958
Jednoga dana...

541
00:46:57,597 --> 00:47:00,994
kupicu loto tiket. Samo jedan.

542
00:47:02,433 --> 00:47:04,271
Naravno, osvojicu dzekpot.

543
00:47:06,189 --> 00:47:08,427
Krstaricamo niz Nil,

544
00:47:09,746 --> 00:47:12,423
plesati na palubi brodica

545
00:47:12,983 --> 00:47:14,901
od jutra do veceri,

546
00:47:15,900 --> 00:47:17,898
gledajuci zalazak sunca

547
00:47:18,338 --> 00:47:19,937
iza piramida!

548
00:47:24,373 --> 00:47:27,330
Stegni me cvrsto, Antoine,
svom snagom!

549
00:47:28,169 --> 00:47:31,046
Stegni mi grudi tako
jako da ne mogu da disem!

550
00:47:33,284 --> 00:47:36,202
Plasi me da jednoga dana neces
zeleti da pleses sa mnom.

551
00:47:37,241 --> 00:47:38,679
Kakva glupost!

552
00:47:39,239 --> 00:47:41,797
Ne zalepiti moj pupak na tvoj?

553
00:47:41,996 --> 00:47:43,315
Ili osetiti tvoju kozu?

554
00:47:44,354 --> 00:47:46,153
Ili milovati tvoja ramena?

555
00:47:47,272 --> 00:47:48,790
Tvoj vrat?

556
00:47:49,749 --> 00:47:50,908
Tvoje dupe?

557
00:47:53,706 --> 00:47:55,424
Znam druge ljude, Antoine,

558
00:47:56,543 --> 00:47:58,461
ali niko nije kao ti.

559
00:48:00,579 --> 00:48:03,017
Nikada nikome nisam pripadala.

560
00:48:04,416 --> 00:48:06,254
Nista ne trazim od tebe.

561
00:48:08,732 --> 00:48:09,611
cvrsto me zagrli!

562
00:48:31,151 --> 00:48:32,350
Pa gospodine Doneker,

563
00:48:32,550 --> 00:48:34,428
koju cete nam danas ispricati?

564
00:48:34,748 --> 00:48:37,186
Tako je dobro znamo,
da nema svrhe.

565
00:48:37,386 --> 00:48:40,543
Da tu je gospodin Doneker.
Vi znate ko je on.

566
00:48:40,982 --> 00:48:44,139
Kladim se da ga se ne secas,
iz meseca u mesec.

567
00:48:44,339 --> 00:48:45,218
cak ni sedmicu.

568
00:48:45,698 --> 00:48:48,256
Istina je da neke od njih
brzo zaboravim,

569
00:48:48,456 --> 00:48:50,893
ali drugih se secam.

570
00:48:51,493 --> 00:48:53,091
Moram ih podnositi dugo vremena.

571
00:48:53,371 --> 00:48:56,448
Zapisivao sam ih,
a onda je prestalo.

572
00:48:57,088 --> 00:48:59,645
To ne znaci mnogo.
U stvari nista,

573
00:49:00,205 --> 00:49:03,122
ali oni nastavljaju da
lutaju po mome secanju.

574
00:49:03,322 --> 00:49:04,361
cujmo jednu.

575
00:49:07,038 --> 00:49:09,117
"U njenoj blistavoj staklenoj palati,

576
00:49:09,756 --> 00:49:11,674
"gde svetlo je neznano,

577
00:49:12,194 --> 00:49:15,111
"Jesi li nasla Boroboudoura,

578
00:49:15,391 --> 00:49:17,669
"kineska princezo?"

579
00:49:18,748 --> 00:49:19,707
Divna je.

580
00:49:20,386 --> 00:49:22,384
Vi uvek kazete da je divno.

581
00:49:23,423 --> 00:49:25,342
Zato sto uvek jeste divno.

582
00:49:25,781 --> 00:49:28,539
Zivo je za trenutak,
a onda nestaje.

583
00:49:29,178 --> 00:49:31,576
Onda jednog dana,
on je prestao da peva,

584
00:49:31,776 --> 00:49:33,215
Moram da pronadjem nove.

585
00:49:34,413 --> 00:49:36,252
Neke me prate po 2 meseca,

586
00:49:36,452 --> 00:49:38,889
ostale nestaju nakon 4 dana.

587
00:49:41,966 --> 00:49:43,605
Boroboudour...

588
00:49:43,805 --> 00:49:46,003
Kineska princeza.

589
00:49:47,601 --> 00:49:50,559
Trebala bi da je poslednja
do kraja sedmice.

590
00:49:51,758 --> 00:49:53,156
Vec bledi,

591
00:49:54,315 --> 00:49:55,994
izgubila je malo od sjaja.

592
00:50:00,629 --> 00:50:01,828
Bice tu druge...

593
00:50:02,827 --> 00:50:04,186
Uvek su bile.

594
00:50:04,985 --> 00:50:06,104
Hvala Bogu.

595
00:50:06,504 --> 00:50:08,742
Neke poslednje, ostale nestaju.

596
00:50:10,380 --> 00:50:13,857
Zaboravio sam onu ranije
ali bilo je nesto kao

597
00:50:14,337 --> 00:50:17,734
"vatrena agonija ruza."
To mi se zalepilo:

598
00:50:17,934 --> 00:50:20,731
"Vatrena agonija ruza."

599
00:50:24,208 --> 00:50:25,886
To je tako dobar osecaj...

600
00:50:27,205 --> 00:50:28,564
Voleo bih da je to poslednja.

601
00:50:28,844 --> 00:50:31,121
Mi nismo u zurbi gospodine Doneker.

602
00:50:52,742 --> 00:50:55,020
"Jesi li srela Boroboudour, a

603
00:50:55,459 --> 00:50:57,417
"kineska princezo?"

604
00:50:59,056 --> 00:51:00,015
Je li to dobro?

605
00:51:00,694 --> 00:51:02,013
Nije prevruce?

606
00:51:54,565 --> 00:51:56,044
Mathildina specijalnost:

607
00:51:56,243 --> 00:51:57,922
nista, nikada nije problem.

608
00:51:58,122 --> 00:51:59,880
Kao da je ona odlucila da oseca

609
00:52:00,080 --> 00:52:02,797
samo prijatne stvari u zivotu.

610
00:52:03,317 --> 00:52:05,355
Dani su prolazili, jedan za drugim,

611
00:52:05,635 --> 00:52:07,074
kao u snu.

612
00:52:14,067 --> 00:52:16,705
Za 10 godina provedenih zajedno,
samo smo se jednom posvadjali,

613
00:52:16,905 --> 00:52:19,262
oko neke gluposti.

614
00:52:20,142 --> 00:52:22,819
citala je kroz

615
00:52:23,019 --> 00:52:24,498
gomilu casopisa.

616
00:52:24,697 --> 00:52:26,536
Gledala je napolje,

617
00:52:26,736 --> 00:52:29,813
ali ulica je toga dana bila nezanimljiva.

618
00:52:30,172 --> 00:52:32,530
Gledala je po praznoj radnji,

619
00:52:33,130 --> 00:52:34,089
a onda mi je rekla:

620
00:52:34,289 --> 00:52:35,647
Zelis li da te osisam?

621
00:52:37,406 --> 00:52:38,085
Voleo bih.

622
00:52:41,042 --> 00:52:44,559
Bio sam,
u Velcro-sealed blue smock...

623
00:52:45,878 --> 00:52:48,236
Dok je sekla moju kosu,
rekla je:

624
00:52:48,875 --> 00:52:51,153
Glumac Fernand Reynaud
vozi jaguara.

625
00:52:51,353 --> 00:52:54,550
Mora da je to videla
u nekom od casopisa.

626
00:52:54,790 --> 00:52:56,668
Kao budala,

627
00:52:56,908 --> 00:52:59,186
sarkasticno sam odgovorio:

628
00:53:00,225 --> 00:53:02,503
Mislis da budala zna kako da vozi?

629
00:53:03,822 --> 00:53:07,338
Nikada ga nisam voleo,
ali Mathilda jeste.

630
00:53:08,058 --> 00:53:10,176
Ona je slegla ramenima,
ljutito uzdahnula

631
00:53:10,416 --> 00:53:11,814
na nacin koji nikada nisam cuo,

632
00:53:12,454 --> 00:53:14,811
i nervozno, tiho, zavrsila sisanje.

633
00:53:16,050 --> 00:53:17,769
Bila je to jedina svadja.

634
00:53:18,768 --> 00:53:20,646
Ali to je sledilo krv u mojim venama.

635
00:53:48,061 --> 00:53:48,860
Upali mi?

636
00:54:25,627 --> 00:54:26,666
Do vraga, matorci!

637
00:54:44,090 --> 00:54:45,369
Sada pusis?

638
00:54:45,928 --> 00:54:46,567
Jesam li te probudio?

639
00:54:48,486 --> 00:54:49,245
Nisam spavala.

640
00:54:50,284 --> 00:54:51,203
Ni ja.

641
00:54:53,161 --> 00:54:56,079
Pusilo mi se.Volim to.

642
00:54:57,597 --> 00:54:59,156
Danas sam kupio kutiju.

643
00:55:18,298 --> 00:55:19,377
Daj mi jednu.

644
00:55:37,001 --> 00:55:37,920
Dobro?

645
00:55:38,600 --> 00:55:39,879
Lepo je.

646
00:55:40,598 --> 00:55:41,797
Zaboravio sam.

647
00:55:44,195 --> 00:55:45,913
Trebalo bi cesce da pusimo.

648
00:55:52,147 --> 00:55:53,306
Izvini za ono.

649
00:55:55,225 --> 00:55:58,541
Ja sam kriva,
Naljutila sam se ni zbog cega.

650
00:56:02,458 --> 00:56:03,577
Je li ti hladno?

651
00:56:05,655 --> 00:56:06,414
Zedna sam.

652
00:56:08,253 --> 00:56:09,092
Hoces li vode?

653
00:56:11,570 --> 00:56:12,649
Zelela bih nesto zestoko.

654
00:56:14,207 --> 00:56:15,606
Sutra cu kupiti nesto.

655
00:56:17,924 --> 00:56:18,683
Imamo kolonjsku.

656
00:56:21,920 --> 00:56:22,799
Otrovaces nas.

657
00:56:23,838 --> 00:56:24,678
Probajmo je.

658
00:56:57,368 --> 00:57:01,204
Dobro dosli u Flamingo Club
na njihove egzoticne koktele!

659
00:57:02,723 --> 00:57:05,320
Probaj ovo... mala damo.

660
00:57:23,464 --> 00:57:24,543
Nije lose.

661
00:57:26,861 --> 00:57:28,020
Daj mi cigaretu.

662
00:57:28,219 --> 00:57:29,658
Prvo, da plesemo.

663
00:57:30,218 --> 00:57:31,456
Radije bih te gledao.

664
00:57:43,006 --> 00:57:44,804
casa! Mogla bi da eksplodira.

665
00:57:45,004 --> 00:57:47,082
- Mislis?
- Ne mozes biti dovoljno oprezan.

666
00:58:08,982 --> 00:58:10,541
Trebalo bi
da kupimo nekoliko pepeljara,

667
00:58:11,100 --> 00:58:13,098
sada kada pusimo.

668
00:58:20,891 --> 00:58:22,450
Tamo je pukotina na plafonu.

669
00:58:30,642 --> 00:58:33,959
Mnogo smo popili. Uvrnute stvari.

670
00:58:34,718 --> 00:58:37,036
Vodili smo ljubav,
stojeci ispred ogledalam.

671
00:58:38,435 --> 00:58:41,472
Trazio sam da zamisli, koliko
parova vodi ljubav u tom momentu

672
00:58:41,672 --> 00:58:43,311
koji je bas tada prolazio,

673
00:58:43,950 --> 00:58:46,308
I u koliko zena su zabijeni kurcevi.

674
00:58:47,746 --> 00:58:49,225
Mnogo hiljada, rekla je ona,

675
00:58:49,425 --> 00:58:51,903
ali nijedna nije tako srecna kao ona.

676
00:58:54,061 --> 00:58:55,859
Dodala je, da nikada
ne bi zelela da me napusti,

677
00:58:56,059 --> 00:58:58,137
i da samo smrt moze da nas rastavi.

678
00:59:22,115 --> 00:59:23,234
Koliko je sati?

679
00:59:26,471 --> 00:59:27,510
Deset.

680
00:59:29,388 --> 00:59:30,987
Mozda bi trebali da ustanemo.

681
00:59:31,826 --> 00:59:33,305
Ako mozemo.

682
00:59:38,340 --> 00:59:39,899
Boli me glava... ovde.

683
00:59:40,978 --> 00:59:42,816
Od losiona za brijanje.

684
00:59:43,376 --> 00:59:45,733
To je bila greska.
Nisi ih trebao mesati.

685
01:00:01,159 --> 01:00:03,597
Oni su otisli. Leto  je.

686
01:00:05,955 --> 01:00:08,313
cekajte me ovde.
Zelim da pozdravim nekoga.

687
01:00:08,512 --> 01:00:11,710
cuvaj brata i sestru.
Budite na trotoaru!

688
01:00:12,429 --> 01:00:13,468
Pazi!

689
01:00:28,015 --> 01:00:30,532
Secas li me se? Gora...

690
01:00:31,531 --> 01:00:33,170
Moja je zena bila takodje ovde, ...

691
01:00:33,969 --> 01:00:34,888
Samar.

692
01:00:35,088 --> 01:00:36,407
Naravno, secam se.

693
01:00:36,607 --> 01:00:39,964
To vas je iznenadilo,
a mi smo malo cavrljali.

694
01:00:40,643 --> 01:00:43,640
Stvari idu na bolje... kod kuce?

695
01:00:43,840 --> 01:00:45,079
Stvari su uzasne.

696
01:00:46,238 --> 01:00:46,997
Vidite ih?

697
01:00:47,557 --> 01:00:49,795
Slatki su. Koliko su stari?

698
01:00:49,994 --> 01:00:51,153
Najmladja se prehladila.

699
01:00:51,953 --> 01:00:55,589
Nikada ranije nije bila bolesna.
Oni svi dobiju,

700
01:00:55,869 --> 01:00:57,108
jedno od drugoga...

701
01:01:01,024 --> 01:01:02,103
Zena ti je otisla?

702
01:01:02,303 --> 01:01:04,461
Da. To se moralo desiti.

703
01:01:05,260 --> 01:01:07,379
Sta da radim sa njima za odmor?

704
01:01:08,138 --> 01:01:09,017
Smislicu nesto.

705
01:01:09,217 --> 01:01:10,696
Vratice se ona.

706
01:01:11,894 --> 01:01:13,613
Nema sanse!

707
01:01:13,813 --> 01:01:15,651
Kada ona nesto umisli...

708
01:01:16,290 --> 01:01:18,249
Kako god, zasluzio sam.

709
01:01:19,527 --> 01:01:20,527
Slatki su, zar ne?

710
01:01:21,366 --> 01:01:23,724
Najstarija je pljunuta majka.

711
01:01:24,603 --> 01:01:25,922
Kako je lepa!

712
01:01:26,121 --> 01:01:27,720
Jos jedno smrcanje.

713
01:01:28,000 --> 01:01:29,678
Vidite? Jedno od drugoga.

714
01:01:29,878 --> 01:01:31,836
Pa, idem ja.

715
01:01:32,036 --> 01:01:34,394
Samo sam zeleo da ih vidim.

716
01:01:35,113 --> 01:01:36,672
Videcemo se ponovo, uskoro...

717
01:01:39,469 --> 01:01:41,028
Mislim da ce se njegova zena vratiti.

718
01:01:41,228 --> 01:01:42,187
Mozda ne.

719
01:01:43,266 --> 01:01:44,984
U redu, deco, idemo.

720
01:01:46,703 --> 01:01:49,500
Znate li
zasto ovaj park ima cudnu boju?

721
01:01:51,778 --> 01:01:54,775
Zato sto ovdasnji ljudi nece
nikada videti nista drugo:

722
01:01:55,734 --> 01:01:57,413
to je njihov poslednji dekor.

723
01:01:58,092 --> 01:02:00,690
To pravi koprenu preko svega:

724
01:02:01,649 --> 01:02:04,127
granja, travnjaka, drveca.

725
01:02:04,326 --> 01:02:06,484
Ne govorite tako, gospodine Isidore.

726
01:02:11,640 --> 01:02:13,158
Upisao sam se u krevet.

727
01:02:13,358 --> 01:02:15,716
Nisam podetinjio,
ucinio sam to namerno.

728
01:02:16,555 --> 01:02:17,514
Zasto?

729
01:02:17,714 --> 01:02:18,753
Da ih gnjavim.

730
01:02:21,591 --> 01:02:25,467
Nisu hteli da pozovu veterinara
za Gris-Gris. Zato je uginuo.

731
01:02:25,947 --> 01:02:27,865
Telefonski poziv bio je
tako velika gnjavaza.

732
01:02:28,065 --> 01:02:30,862
Sada svakodnevno moraju da
menjaju moje carsave.

733
01:02:31,541 --> 01:02:33,660
Mogu ja i gore, ako me nateraju.

734
01:02:33,899 --> 01:02:36,617
Nemoj da vas strpaju u bolnicu.

735
01:02:42,731 --> 01:02:43,650
Kako je radnja?

736
01:02:44,729 --> 01:02:47,727
Dobro. Antoine planira
da okreci tavanicu.

737
01:02:47,926 --> 01:02:50,884
Prvo belo, pa satenski finis.
Stvari ce biti svetlije.

738
01:02:57,518 --> 01:02:59,116
Bedno je ovde.

739
01:03:01,034 --> 01:03:04,551
Lose je sto je zadnja stvar koju
cu videti tako bedna.

740
01:03:10,945 --> 01:03:12,144
Prijatelji?

741
01:03:14,702 --> 01:03:15,941
U tvojim godinama,

742
01:03:16,181 --> 01:03:19,138
mislis da su svi stari ljudi
prijatelji zato sto su stari.

743
01:03:19,697 --> 01:03:20,736
To nije istina.

744
01:03:22,415 --> 01:03:25,212
Mogu ti reci iz iskustva:

745
01:03:25,412 --> 01:03:26,931
stare seronje su najgore.

746
01:03:27,131 --> 01:03:28,849
Ovo ih je mesto puno,

747
01:03:29,049 --> 01:03:31,247
ukljucujuci i mene.

748
01:03:33,005 --> 01:03:36,002
Hajde, otpraticu vas do kapije.

749
01:03:36,202 --> 01:03:38,760
Imamo mnogo vremena.
Dosli smo da vas vidimo.

750
01:03:42,756 --> 01:03:44,794
Vidjam mnogo rodbine koja nedeljom,

751
01:03:45,194 --> 01:03:46,393
zuri da ode,

752
01:03:47,232 --> 01:03:49,670
brze nego sto je ovamo dosla.

753
01:03:50,389 --> 01:03:53,027
Razumem ja -
zivot ne pripada ovde.

754
01:03:54,985 --> 01:03:57,343
Videces,
bolje cete se osecati napolju,

755
01:03:57,982 --> 01:03:59,541
ne mozes pomoci,

756
01:04:00,220 --> 01:04:02,258
Uzdahnuces sa olaksanjem.

757
01:04:08,732 --> 01:04:10,771
Dolazim svakoga dana
i otvaram kapiju.

758
01:04:10,970 --> 01:04:13,368
Osecam se tako, kao da
mogu da odem, ako zelim.

759
01:04:18,603 --> 01:04:19,842
Do vidjenja, gospodine Agopian.

760
01:04:20,082 --> 01:04:21,041
Zdravo Antoine.

761
01:04:23,239 --> 01:04:24,558
Ostanite srecni.

762
01:04:26,436 --> 01:04:27,995
Setite me se ponekad.

763
01:04:45,699 --> 01:04:49,135
Nista nije brze od smrti.

764
01:04:50,015 --> 01:04:54,371
Zaglavis se sa lekovima, mislis
da si ok, i u sekundi, odletis!

765
01:04:54,770 --> 01:04:57,128
cak ni ne odletis:
"O, u ODLETIS i TRAS"!

766
01:04:57,368 --> 01:05:01,164
Kazem da je to kao da si
zaspao bez snova.

767
01:05:02,044 --> 01:05:05,001
Ali kada zaspes, onda se i
probudis. Zato i spavas.

768
01:05:05,281 --> 01:05:07,439
Ako zauvek zaspis,
ne mozes reci

769
01:05:07,758 --> 01:05:08,438
da si zaspao.

770
01:05:08,677 --> 01:05:10,955
U svakom slucaju si nesvestan,
zar ne?

771
01:05:11,275 --> 01:05:13,073
Nemas svest ni o cemu.

772
01:05:13,393 --> 01:05:15,831
To nije isto!

773
01:05:16,311 --> 01:05:19,228
Mesaju se"nicega svestan"
i "nesvestan",

774
01:05:19,468 --> 01:05:21,466
i razgovor malaksava.

775
01:05:21,785 --> 01:05:23,504
Vidis li razliku?

776
01:05:23,824 --> 01:05:26,701
Ako ne, zasto do vraga pricati?

777
01:05:26,941 --> 01:05:28,419
O cemu smo govorili?

778
01:05:29,059 --> 01:05:30,937
Sta vi mislite, gospodine Antoine?

779
01:05:33,335 --> 01:05:35,733
Smrt je zuta i sa ukusom vanile.

780
01:05:39,529 --> 01:05:40,408
Jeste li sigurni u to?

781
01:05:42,526 --> 01:05:43,925
Mogu da se kladim u to.

