01:06:26,806 --> 01:06:27,685
Uzasno.

790
01:06:28,564 --> 01:06:30,483
Svaki dan je sve pogureniji.

791
01:06:31,402 --> 01:06:33,240
Svaki dan je sve stariji.

792
01:06:35,278 --> 01:06:36,717
Zivot je odvratan.

793
01:06:41,113 --> 01:06:42,512
Sprema se oluja.

794
01:07:06,769 --> 01:07:07,449
Nema svetla!

795
01:07:08,368 --> 01:07:10,126
Pokvarices oci.

796
01:07:10,965 --> 01:07:12,164
citam.

797
01:07:14,203 --> 01:07:16,001
Zelim da sednes gde uvek sedis.

798
01:09:13,453 --> 01:09:15,092
Kupicu jogurt za veceras.

799
01:09:53,337 --> 01:09:54,216
"Moja ljubavi,

800
01:09:55,814 --> 01:09:57,613
"Odlazim, pre nego sto ti odes.

801
01:09:59,091 --> 01:10:01,409
"Odlazim pre nego sto
tvoja zudnja nestane.

802
01:10:02,289 --> 01:10:04,686
"Tada cemo biti ostavljeni
ljubavi, sami ,

803
01:10:05,885 --> 01:10:08,363
"i znacemo da to nije dovoljno.

804
01:10:10,601 --> 01:10:12,519
"Odlazim pre nego sto
postanem nesrecna.

805
01:10:14,677 --> 01:10:17,115
"Idem noseci ukus nasih zagrljaja,

806
01:10:18,074 --> 01:10:19,633
"tvoj miris,

807
01:10:19,832 --> 01:10:20,911
"tvoj izgled,

808
01:10:21,631 --> 01:10:22,710
"tvoje poljupce.

809
01:10:24,388 --> 01:10:27,665
