"Ljubim te sada tako
nezno da cu od toga umreti.

812
01:10:38,335 --> 01:10:39,814
"Uvek cu te voleti.

813
01:10:40,494 --> 01:10:41,852
"Samo sam tebe i volela.

814
01:10:44,290 --> 01:10:46,568
"Idem tako
da me nikada neces zaboraviti...

815
01:10:48,446 --> 01:10:49,405
"Mathilda."

816
01:12:26,514 --> 01:12:28,033
Hocete li pranje?

817
01:13:18,950 --> 01:13:20,349
Ko vas je naucio da igrate?

818
01:13:20,549 --> 01:13:22,987
Niko. Izmislio sam.
Uvek sam to voleo.

819
01:13:23,306 --> 01:13:25,464
Ne tako brzo! Pokazacu vam.

820
01:13:49,970 --> 01:13:51,888
Niste losi.

821
01:13:52,208 --> 01:13:53,327
Mislite?

